[{'content': 'what are signs of congestive heart failure?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'It can be very hard to determine if someone has congestive heart failure, but the symptoms can include shortness of breath, chest pain, and swelling in the feet, legs, or abdomen.  This is sometimes called edema.  The heart itself can also be damaged, causing it to beat irregularly.', 'role': 'assistant'}
 {'content': 'Anything else I should look up for?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'I suggest that you go to WebMD, or google "congestive heart failure symptoms".  You could also go to the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention’s Web site.', 'role': 'assistant'}
 {'content': 'Okay, thanks. Do you have any other tips?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'I have two other thoughts.  First, if someone you know is showing any symptoms of congestive heart failure, please talk to them about the possibility of seeing a doctor.  Second, if you’re ever worried about having congestive heart failure yourself, I’d encourage you to consult a doctor.', 'role': 'assistant'}]

[{'content': 'How do I make my hair more soft and silky?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'I think there are a few different approaches you can take.  First, what you can do on your own is keep it clean, and let it air dry naturally when you shower.  You can also use a conditioner in shampoo that will moisturize it and make it smoother and shinier.  And of course, many of the things you do with your hair also affect the health of your scalp and hair follicles.  For example, sometimes the scalp can become dry and flaky due to genetics or environmental factors, and that can make the hair more brittle and even make it appear to look dry or flaky.  You can also use oils on your scalp and hair to keep them hydrated and healthy, and this helps the hair look better as well.  You can use your fingers to rub oil into your scalp, or you can use a hair oil that you pour onto your hair before shampooing.', 'role': 'assistant'}
 {'content': 'What kind of hair oil do you recommend?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'There are a few different types of oil.  Ones with coconut oil or olive oil are very good for hair because they contain fatty acids that help to make the hair healthier and stronger.  However, hair oils can also include things like tea tree oil or peppermint oil that are very moisturizing for the scalp and hair, and that can make the hair feel thicker and more healthy as well.  It’s a good idea to use oil that has all three of these properties, which may not be easy to find but they do exist.  You can also use oils on your scalp after shampooing by spreading it onto your hair and onto your scalp.  For example, if you use coconut oil for the hair, you can use almond oil for the scalp.  Or vice versa.  You can also massage your hair with the oil to help increase its penetration into the hair strands and make the hair appear glossy', 'role': 'assistant'}]

[{'content': 'How do I make hair bows?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'You can start with a strip of fabric or a piece of cardboard.  Wrap it around a mold or form, and secure it with straight pins or glue.  Make sure it’s completely smooth and the edges are tucked in.  Cut the ends at an angle, so they stand straight up.  To make a bow shape, cut two pieces of fabric, each about three inches long and an inch or so wide, and fold them in half lengthwise.  Place one end of each strip into the center of the bow head, and fold the other end up to meet it.  Secure the center with straight pins or glue, and then glue or sew the folded ends to the head to create a bow shape.', 'role': 'assistant'}
 {'content': "I don't think cardboard is realistic.", 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': "Sure, you can always make a molded plastic shape and set it inside a piece of fabric, or you can make a two-sided piece of fabric and fold it over to create a bow shape.  The molded plastic option is probably a little more sturdy than the handmade approach, but they're both pretty easy and straightforward.", 'role': 'assistant'}]

[{'content': 'How do you play the violin?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'You need to place your violin under your chin, and position your left hand so that your fingers are on the correct strings.  Then you’ll need to place your bow on the strings.  Using the bow, you’ll need to get the right tempo and timing, and you’ll need to make sure the violin is singing.', 'role': 'assistant'}
 {'content': 'What are the different parts of a violin?', 'role': 'user'}
 {'content': 'The body of the violin is where the sound comes from.  You’ll place your chin on the violin to begin to play.  The top of the violin, also referredded to as the bridge, is where the strings are attached.  The strings themselves run from the bridge down to the body of the violin.  You’ll need to position your left hand correctly on the strings.  And you’ll need a bow to get the right timing and rhythm to make the violin sing.', 'role': 'assistant'}]

