 {'content': 'Glad you asked!  Dwayne Johnson has enjoyed a long and successful career as an actor in Hollywood films.  His best-known roles include The Rock, which is one of his most successful films, and Hercules, a Greek mythological character who received an updated take in this film.  Johnson also starred in the films Jumanji, Faster, and Bad Boys II.  Some other notable films in which he’s appeared include Journey 2: The Mysterious Island, Doom, San Andreas, and G.I. Joe: Retaliation.', 'role': 'assistant'}
