-Prepare and plan for restful sleep by reducing your stress levels before bed, practice relaxation techniques such as deep breathing exercises, meditating, and progressive muscle relaxation. Engage in calming activities previously in your day, skipping television, work or multitasking in the hours leading up to bed time. Try to avoid frustrating or', 'role': 'assistant'}
